{"tid":1992483,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有冇人話我知2017年呢一日香港南邊有冇國家發射過穿梭機?","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T10:15:09.000Z","uid":279952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d81924215d16b880cdf2de6983e44e770b03c96","tid":1992483,"uid":279952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/om18ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fom18ba&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=a64a922b\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/om18ba</a><br />\n拍攝日期: 30/9/2017 13:03分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5ckKgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5ckKgs.jpg&h=90f4daac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位置圖<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n<br />\n個日出去食野見個天有物體垂直升空 <br />\n望真D似穿梭機<br />\n無聊拍低左 之後冇件事 <br />\n但點解忽然而家問返<br />\n因為前排夢見返個日畫面 問自己點解唔搵下當時果部係咩黎<br />\n之後Google極都搵唔到相關資料 (搵日期+升空等字眼)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQ878Ly.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQ878Ly.jpg&h=3ca1a99f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n香港南面有菲律賓 印尼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人話我知 等我有個解脫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d1a44a333d64b0404aeefc912990d609cf6c41","tid":1992483,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f85f802421fa8b85a7b9adfc2049580358488a80","tid":1992483,"uid":279952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:37:16.000Z","msg":"求幫推"},{"pid":"01a1c1675de7736d8ba911b11c97ea6dc9ac9518","tid":1992483,"uid":279952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm